# Service Desk User Stories (ITSM)

## Story 1: Create Incident
As a user,
I want to submit an issue,
So that IT can resolve it quickly.

### Acceptance Criteria
- Mandatory fields: Category, Description, Impact
- Ticket number assigned automatically

---

## Story 2: Track Incident
As a user,
I want to check my ticket status,
So that I know the progress.

### Acceptance Criteria
- Status visible: Open, In Progress, Resolved
